-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_forca_vendas
-- AS
SELECT
    [BU]
,[DIVISAO]
,[NOME_GD]
,[NOME_GR]
,[NOME_REPRESENTANTE]
,[MUDID]
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]
,[TERRITORIO]
,[TERRITORIO_GD]
,[TERRITORIO_GR]
,[CICLO_FV]
,[ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO]
,[FLAG_PROJETO]
,[FLAG_TARGET]
,[KEY_TERR_CICLO]
,[KEY_CICLO_TERR_GD]
,[KEY_DIVISAO_CICLO]
,[KEY_MUDID_TERR]
,[KEY_TERR]
,[CIDADE_ZONA]
,[UF_ZONA]
,[CHAVE]
,[ZONA_COMPLETA]
,[CHAVE_ZONA]
,[ZONA]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_forca_vendas.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
       [BU]						 VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIVISAO]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_GD]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_GR]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_REPRESENTANTE]        VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MUDID]                     VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]         VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO]                VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_GD]             VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_GR]             VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CICLO_FV]                  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO]        VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[FLAG_PROJETO]              VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[FLAG_TARGET]               VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_TERR_CICLO]            VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_CICLO_TERR_GD]         VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_DIVISAO_CICLO]         VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_MUDID_TERR]            VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_TERR]                  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CIDADE_ZONA]               VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[UF_ZONA]                   VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CHAVE]                     VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ZONA_COMPLETA]             VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CHAVE_ZONA]                VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ZONA]                      VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
